  "title": "Staff Nurse (Hospital, Inpatient ward) - Entry level [GC]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist doctor during consultation adn in performing necessary procedures.</li>\n  <li>Perform general nursing duties which includes performing of clinical procedure/patient’s vital signs monitoring.</li>\n  <li>Provide education and counselling to patients prior to treatment.</li>\n  <li>Assist in reception duties, registration, collecting payment.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance to infection control and nursing policies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>With a minimum of Diploma in Nursing.</li>\n  <li>SNB registered Staff Nurse.</li>\n  <li>Training is provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
